99
00:08:57,968 --> 00:09:01,567
Oh, you have to fill out
your own menu card.

100
00:09:04,012 --> 00:09:08,381
"One macedoine of fruit,
beef Oriental, rice, carrots...

101
00:09:08,381 --> 00:09:11,078
coffee, apple pie a la mode. "

102
00:09:12,154 --> 00:09:13,644
You print very well.

103
00:09:15,490 --> 00:09:16,479
Thanks.

104
00:09:17,492 --> 00:09:20,222
I'll have the same thing.
You do it for me.

105
